Package powergrid.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigureFrame
    Frame that holds the run and cancel buttons along with the Task's Configuration panel.
    ControlPanel
    Control Panel that allows control and overview of PowerGrid functionality.
    DestinationPanel
    This Panel shows an available destination, and a button that orders the Bot to travel to this destination when clicked.
    MapViewer
    Canvas that the WorldMap is printed on to show the mapped areas in the Grid.
    TaskConfigurationPanel
    This abstract class is meant as a supertype for the configuration panel of Tasks.
    TaskPanel
    This Panel shows all available tasks of each Loaded Plugin.
    TaskPanel.TaskEntry  
    TravelPanel
    This Panel shows the available destinations and allows the user to search for specific entries using a text field.
